1995;;The Immortals;;American;;Brian Grant;;Eric Roberts, Tia Carrere, Tony Curtis;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Immortals_(1995_film);;A crafty nightclub owner (Jack) brings together a group of small-time hoods and teams them up in unusual pairs (black man and white racist, Ivy Leaguer and simpleton) for a set of multiple heists which turn out to be an elaborate double cross against a notorious gangster (Dominic). During an extended standoff in a nightclub between Jack and his band of thieves and Dominic's henchman, the hoods discover why Jack brought them all together for what amounts to a suicidal mission.